== 製作 ==
2019年2月26日，[[索尼動畫|索尼動畫]]宣佈正在開發《尖叫旅社4》<ref>{{cite web |first=Matt |last=Donnelly |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/hotel-transylvania-4-to-hit-theaters-in-december-2021-1203150290/ |title='Hotel Transylvania 4' to Hit Theaters in December 2021 |date=2019-02-26 |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |access-date=2019-09-19 |archive-date=2019-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929121923/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/hotel-transylvania-4-to-hit-theaters-in-december-2021-1203150290/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年10月4日，確認[[格恩迪·塔塔科夫斯基|格恩迪·塔塔科夫斯基]]不會回歸執導電影<ref>{{cite web|first=Dave|last=Trumbore|title='Hotel Transylvania 4': Genndy Tartakovsky Confirms He Won't Be in the Director's Chair|url=https://collider.com/hotel-transylvania-4-director-genndy-tartakovsky/|date=2019-10-04|website=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]]|access-date=2019-10-23|archive-date=2019-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007072722/https://collider.com/hotel-transylvania-4-director-genndy-tartakovsky/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年9月17日，宣佈《[[尖叫旅社2|尖叫旅社2]]》及《[[尖叫旅社3：怪獸假期|尖叫旅社3：怪獸假期]]》的分鏡師珍妮佛·克魯斯卡以及《[[海綿寶寶|海綿寶寶]]》和《[[探險活寶|探險活寶]]》的製作人{{le|德瑞克·卓瑪|Derek Drymon}}將擔任《尖叫旅社4》的導演，而塔塔科夫斯基撰寫劇本<ref>{{cite web |last=Donnelly |first=Matt |title=Selena Gomez Upped to Executive Producer for 'Hotel Transylvania 4', Returns as Female Lead (EXCLUSIVE) |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/selena-gomez-hotel-transylvania-4-executive-producer-star-1234773619/ |access-date=2020-09-17 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2020-09-17 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919201123/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/selena-gomez-hotel-transylvania-4-executive-producer-star-1234773619/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/1149155-hotel-transylvania-4-still-set-for-2021-debut |title='Hotel Transylvania 4' Set for 2021 Debut with Selena Gomez Returning |website=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]] |first=Maggie |last=Dela Paz |date=2020-09-18 |access-date=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031170559/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/1149155-hotel-transylvania-4-still-set-for-2021-debut |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年4月9日，公佈正式片名為《Hotel Transylvania: Transformania》<ref>{{cite web |last=Fuster |first=Jeremy |url=https://www.thewrap.com/hotel-transylvania-4-gets-full-title-moves-up-release-date-to-july/ |title=‘Hotel Transylvania 4’ Gets Full Title, Moves Up Release Date to July |work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |date=2021-04-09 |access-date=2021-04-09 |archive-date=2021-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430134003/https://www.thewrap.com/hotel-transylvania-4-gets-full-title-moves-up-release-date-to-july/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《尖叫旅社4》由[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影視娛樂]]原定於2021年10月1日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/hotel-transylvania-transformania-delay-october-1235000545/ |title='Hotel Transylvania: Transformania' Moves to October |website=[[Variety|Variety]] |first=Ellise |last=Shafer |date=2021-06-18 |access-date=2021-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618214630/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/hotel-transylvania-transformania-delay-october-1235000545/ |archive-date=2021-06-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年8月16日，索尼影視娛樂宣佈本片取消院線上映，改為直接在[[Amazon_Prime_Video|Amazon Prime Video]]上線<ref name="Amazon">{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/horror/news/sony-movies-skip-theaters-hotel-transylvania-4-streaming-amazon/ |title=Sony Skips Theaters With Hotel Transylvania 4, Streaming on Amazon Instead |website=[[ComicBook.com|ComicBook.com]] |last=Anderson |first=Jenna |date=2021-08-16 |access-date=2021-08-16 |archive-date=2021-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816210600/https://comicbook.com/horror/news/sony-movies-skip-theaters-hotel-transylvania-4-streaming-amazon/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。此前，上映日期曾定於2021年8月6日、2021年12月22日以及2021年7月23日<ref>{{cite web |last=Bean |first=Travis |title='Spider-Man 3' And 'Spider-Man: Into The Spider-Verse 2' Get New Release Dates |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/travisbean/2020/04/24/spider-man-3-and-spider-man-into-the-spider-verse-2-get-new-release-dates/#246844d537ef |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |date=2020-04-24 |access-date=2020-04-24 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425045742/https://www.forbes.com/sites/travisbean/2020/04/24/spider-man-3-and-spider-man-into-the-spider-verse-2-get-new-release-dates/#246844d537ef |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/hotel-transylvania-4-christmas-2021-1202565733/ |title='Hotel Transylvania 4' To Open Doors Christmas Season 2021 |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2019-02-26 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2019-09-19 |archive-date=2019-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806050310/https://deadline.com/2019/02/hotel-transylvania-4-christmas-2021-1202565733/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2021/04/hotel-transylvania-transformania-opening-earlier-this-summer-1234730969/ |title=‘Hotel Transylvania: Transformania’ Opening Earlier This Summer |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2021-04-09 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2021-04-09 |archive-date=2021-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409151604/https://deadline.com/2021/04/hotel-transylvania-transformania-opening-earlier-this-summer-1234730969/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年10月，電影於2022年1月14日上線<ref name="January2022">{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/hotel-transylvania-4-amazon-sony-january-premiere-date-1235081967/ |title='Hotel Transylvania 4' Heads To Amazon, Sets January Release Date |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |last=Aurthur |first=Kate |date=2021-10-06 |access-date=2021-10-06 |archive-date=2021-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211006194513/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/hotel-transylvania-4-amazon-sony-january-premiere-date-1235081967/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。2022年4月3日，影片在中国大陆上映<ref name="China_release"/>。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據73條評論，本片獲得52%的新鮮度，平均得分5.3／10，觀眾投票獲得42%的分數，平均得分為3／5<ref>{{Cite Rotten Tomatoes|title=Hotel Transylvania: Transformania |id=hotel_transylvania_transformania|type=movie|access-date=2022-01-14}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得46分<ref>{{Cite Metacritic|id=hotel-transylvania-transformania|type=movie|title=Hotel Transylvania: Transformania|access-date=2022-01-14}}</ref>。

